 <h2 class="section-title text-center">What Is a Qi2 Magnetic Wireless Car Charger Mount?</h2>
 <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">A Qi2 magnetic car charger mount combines a <strong>phone holder and wireless fast charger</strong> into one automotive accessory. Built around the Qi2 MPP (Magnetic Power Profile) standard with <strong>N52H neodymium magnets</strong>, modern car mounts deliver 15W-25W wireless charging with perfect magnetic snap alignment — eliminating the need to fumble with cables while driving. For B2B buyers, the wireless car charger mount aftermarket is the <strong>fastest-growing segment in automotive charging</strong> — 50% of new cars now ship with wireless charging built in, but over 1 billion vehicles on the road today do not, creating a massive retrofit opportunity.</p>

